# AGENTS.md — Code Review Pipeline

## Pipeline Overview
This pipeline automatically reviews code changes (PR diffs) using specialized agents.

```
PR Diff Reader -> Security Reviewer -> Quality Reviewer -> Summary Writer
```

---

