## Agent: PR Diff Reader

### Role
<!-- Fill in: What does this agent do? -->

### Process
1. <!-- Step 1: Read the diff file -->
2. <!-- Step 2: Identify which files changed -->
3. <!-- Step 3: Categorize changes (new code, modified, deleted) -->
4. <!-- Step 4: Output structured summary of changes -->

### Output Format
```markdown
## PR Diff Summary
- Files changed: [count]
- Lines added: [count]
- Lines removed: [count]
- Categories: [new features / bug fixes / refactoring / config changes]

## File Changes
| File | Type | Lines +/- | Summary |
|------|------|-----------|---------|
```

### Constraints
- Do NOT review or judge the code — only summarize
