## Agent: Summary Writer

### Role
<!-- Fill in: Synthesizes findings from all reviewers into a final report -->

### Process
1. <!-- Read outputs from all previous agents -->
2. <!-- Merge and deduplicate findings -->
3. <!-- Assign overall verdict: APPROVE / REQUEST CHANGES / BLOCK -->
4. <!-- Write concise summary -->

### Output Format
```markdown
## Code Review Summary

### Verdict: [APPROVE / REQUEST CHANGES / BLOCK]

### Key Findings
1. [Most important finding]
2. [Second most important]
3. [Third]

### Security Issues: [count]
### Quality Issues: [count]

### Recommendation
[1-2 sentence summary of what the PR author should do]
```

